    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name>Teudiperto</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie
                            Deusdedit</persName> permuta beni con <persName ref="#people/3319"
                            key="#Bishops">Iacobo</persName> in Dei nomine huius <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68">sancte Lucensis ecclesie</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> (…). Teudiperto cede: duo petiis de terris
                        et uno petio de virgario meo, quam abeo in loco <placeName ref="#places/36"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads"
                            >Saltucclo</placeName>, qui una ex ipse petia de terra <rs
                            key="#Confinia">uno latere tene</rs> in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Churches">Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>, uno caput et uno lato tene in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, et alio caput tene in terra
                                <persName><name>Agelmundi</name></persName>; ille alia petia uno
                        caput tene in vinea ipsius ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Churches">Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>, et alio caput tene cum uno lato in <rs key="#Roads"
                            >via publica</rs>, alio lato tene in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra
                            regis</rs>; et ipsi virgario est tenente ambas latera in virgario
                        predicte ecclesie Sancti Fridiani, et amba capita tene in virgario meo, quam
                        in mea reservo potestate (…); il tutto [cum] arboribus suis. (…). Riceve in
                        cambio: duo petiis de terris et uno petio de virgario, que est pertenens
                        eidem ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Churches">Sancti
                            Frigiani</orgName>, quam abetis in loco <placeName ref="#places/36"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >Saltucclo</placeName>, et est tenente una ex ipse petie de terra uno
                        caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput cum uno lato tene in
                        terra mea, et alio latus tene in terra ecclesie <orgName key="#Churches"
                            >Sancti Mamiliani</orgName>; et illa alia petiola est tenente uno caput
                        et ambas latera similiter in terra mea q.s. Teudipert, et alio caput tene in
                            <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, et sunt per mensura <rs key="#Size"
                            >plus minus sistariorum quattuordecim</rs>; et ipsi virgario est tenente
                        ambas capita et uno lato in terra mea q.s. Teudipert, alio lato tene in
                        terra ipsius ecclesie vestre Sancti Frigiani. (…) Ubi super hoc concambium
                        direxisti <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missus vester</rs>,
                        idest <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Other_clerics"
                                ><name>Emmulum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, qui ambulavit et previdit qualiter
                        melioratum cambium dedi vobis a parte ipsius ecclesie quam dedissem.
                            <persName key="#Writer #Priests"><name>Richiprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >viganationis cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Oltre al misso del vescovo sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testimoni</rs>: <persName key="#Witness"
                            ><name>Alateus</name></persName> filio
                            <persName><name>Minti</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> filio
                            <persName><name>Gumprandi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Simeon</name></persName> filio Teuderadis,
                        Alamundus, Tacolfus  <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
